脓癣（Kerion Celsi）是由[[皮癣菌|皮癣菌]]感染头皮及毛囊并继发细菌感染的化脓性[[皮癣菌病|皮癣菌病]]，是皮癣菌病的最严重形式。<ref>{{cite book|last= 中国头癣诊疗指南工作组 |title= 中国头癣诊断和治疗指南（２０１８修订版）。中国真菌学杂志 2019年2月 第14卷 第1期 4-6页， Chin J Mycol，Feburary 2019, 14 (1): 4-6.|url=http://medi-guide.meditool.cn/ymtpdf/C417B644-DF11-7918-A026-F979818DCF68.pdf}}</ref>  <ref>{{cite book|last= R Vanbreuseghem, C D Vroey |title= Systemic opportunistic fungal infections. Postgrad Med J 1979 Sep;55(647):593-4. doi: 10.1136/pgmj.55.647.593. |url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2425664/pdf/postmedj00249-0012.pdf}}</ref> <ref>{{cite book|last=Uprety, Shraddha; Sharma, Ramesh|title=Kerion — A Boggy Lump. New England Journal of Medicine. 375 (10): 980.|url=https://www.nejm.org/doi/10.1056/NEJMicm1514152|access-date=2021-02-26|archive-date=2019-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190409090109/https://www.nejm.org/doi/10.1056/NEJMicm1514152|dead-url=no}}</ref> 最常见罹患部位是头皮，但也可发生在暴露于真菌的任何其他部位，如面部（[[头癣|头癣]]）与上肢（[[体癣|体癣]]）。脓癣常由[[白癣|白癣]]或[[黑点癣|黑点癣]]发展而来，约80%的脓癣由犬[[小孢癣菌|小孢癣菌]]（Microsporum canis）引起。脓癣必须口服[[抗真菌药|抗真菌药]]治疗才能痊愈，局部用药无效。脓癣经常被误诊为[[细菌性脓肿|细菌性脓肿]]，一旦采用手术切开引流，则会迁延不愈。<ref>{{cite book|last=李若瑜|title=脓癣该怎么治疗？-医学微视 |url=https://www.mvyxws.com/vod/play/id/21218}}</ref> <ref>{{cite book|last=Vikash Paudel,|title=Surgery of Kerion, a Nightmare for Nondermatologists, Case Reports in Dermatological Medicine, vol. 2020, Article ID 8825912, 3 pages, 2020.|url=https://www.hindawi.com/journals/cridm/2020/8825912/|access-date=2021-02-26|archive-date=2020-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201125015/https://www.hindawi.com/journals/cridm/2020/8825912/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

脓癣也叫[[脓癣|凯氏蜂窝病]] （{{le|Kerion}} Celsi），由[[古罗马|古罗马]]医学家、百科全书编纂家[[凯尔苏斯|凯尔苏斯]]率先在他的八卷巨著《医术》（{{le|De Medicina}}）中描述。

除了[[皮癣菌|皮癣菌]]外，其他真菌能够导致脓癣。中国[[广州|广州]]医院报道[[隆起曲霉菌|隆起曲霉菌]]（[[Aspergillus_protuberus|Aspergillus protuberus]]）引发脓癣。<ref>{{cite book|last=Jia, J., Chen, M., Mo, X. et al.|title=The first case report of kerion-type scalp mycosis caused by Aspergillus protuberus. BMC Infect Dis 19, 506 (2019).|url=https://bmcinfectdis.biomedcentral.com/articles/10.1186/s12879-019-4144-7|access-date=2021-02-26|archive-date=2020-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204173925/https://bmcinfectdis.biomedcentral.com/articles/10.1186/s12879-019-4144-7|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==临床表现==
引起脓癣的真菌多为嗜动物型，少数为嗜人型或嗜地型菌株，因此人类机体对这些[[皮癣菌|皮癣菌]]感染发生剧烈的炎症性与肉芽肿性反应。脓癣多发生于儿童，尤其是学龄前儿童。最初表现为化脓性毛囊炎，群集性小脓疱融合形成结节或肿块，界限清楚，质地柔软，表面有与毛囊口一致的小脓点。当肿块变大后则呈现蜂窝状或海绵状，挤压时有多孔溢脓现象。如果形成瘘，脓液也可从瘘道流出。可见局部淋巴结肿大。肿块常伴随炎症反应，如红、肿、热、痛。毛发稀疏并脱落，导致秃顶。少数患者会因发烧而全身不适。可能会出现广泛的瘙痒性湿疹样皮疹。<ref>{{cite book|last=L. C. Fuller; F. J. Child; G. Midgley; E. M. Higgins.|title=Diagnosis and management of scalp ringworm. BMJ. 326 (7388): 539–541. doi:10.1136/bmj.326.7388.539.|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC1125423/|access-date=2021-02-26|archive-date=2022-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220221215040/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC1125423/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
==病因==
引起脓癣的真菌多为嗜动物型，少数为嗜人型或嗜地型菌株。这些致病菌株包括犬[[小孢癣菌|小孢癣菌]]（Microsporum canis）、石膏状小孢癣菌（M. gypseum）、 [[断发毛癣菌|断发毛癣菌]]（Trichophyton tonsurans）、疣状毛癣菌（T. verrucosum）与下颔毛癣菌（T. mentagrophytes）等。红色毛癣菌（T. rubrum）不是脓癣的常见原因。<ref>{{cite book|last=Reyes IAF, Vega DC, Arriaga LFR, et al. |title=Kerion celsi caused by microsporum gypseum: report of two cases and review.  J Dermat Cosmetol 2018;2(3):151-157. DOI:10.15406/jdc.2018.02.00066|url=https://medcraveonline.com/JDC/kerion-celsi-caused-by-microsporum-gypseum-report-of-two-cases-and-review.html}}</ref> <ref>{{cite book|last=Annemay Chollet, Vincent Cattin, Marina Fratti, Bernard Mignon, Michel Monod. |title=Which Fungus Originally was Trichophyton mentagrophytes? Historical Review and Illustration by a Clinical Case. Mycopathologia (2015) 180:1–5 DOI 10.1007/s11046-015-9893-2.|url=https://citeseerx.ist.psu.edu/viewdoc/download?doi=10.1.1.1002.4018&rep=rep1&type=pdf}}</ref>

==诊断==
根据临床表现与体征，可初步作出脓癣的诊断。确诊有赖于显微镜检查和真菌培养，样品为取自患处的刮屑和毛发。同时也应采集细菌拭子作涂片观察和培养。<ref>{{cite book|last=Reyes IAF, Vega DC, Arriaga LFR, et al. |title=Kerion celsi caused by microsporum gypseum: report of two cases and review. J Dermat Cosmetol. 2018;2(3):151-157. DOI:10.15406/jdc.2018.02.00066|url=https://medcraveonline.com/JDC/kerion-celsi-caused-by-microsporum-gypseum-report-of-two-cases-and-review.html}}</ref>

==传染性==
脓癣可以传染到自己身体的其他部位，或任何与其接触的人，如家人、同学、朋友等。不要与他人共用被褥和毛巾。不要接触宠物如猫、狗等，以免通过动物感染家人。梳子和发刷应消毒或丢弃，以防止传染或自我再感染。<ref>{{cite book|last=L Trovato et al (2019)|title=Molecular diagnosis of kerion celsi caused by Trichophyton tonsurans in a Italian child.|url=https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s11046-016-0058-8#citeas|access-date=2021-02-26|archive-date=2018-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180610052703/https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007%2Fs11046-016-0058-8#citeas|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==治疗==
脓癣必须口服抗真菌药治疗，通常至少要开6-8周的疗程。局部用抗真菌剂无效，因为真菌深深侵入毛囊。[[灰黄霉素|灰黄霉素]]仍为首选，也可使用[[特比萘芬|特比萘芬]]、[[伊曲康唑|伊曲康唑]]。如果存在细菌感染，则需要使用抗生素。含有酮康唑或环吡酮的抗真菌洗发剂有助于降低传染他人的风险。切忌手术切开引流，否则会迁延不愈。<ref>{{cite book|last=Hay, R.J. |title=Molecular diagnosis of kerion celsi caused by Trichophyton tonsurans in an Italian child. Med Mycol Case Rep. 2019 Jun; 24: 72–74.|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC6503126/}}</ref>

==预后==
绝大多数脓癣患者经口服抗真菌药治疗可以痊愈。头发在治疗后会重新长出，但长期得不到医治者可能导致永久性脱发。

